{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/pullrequests/67/comments/11990029.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/diff/traversaro/ign-math:933a4526672f..c6a20f99810f?path=src%2FCMakeLists.txt"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/pull-requests/67/_/diff#comment-11990029"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 67, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/pullrequests/67.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-math/pull-requests/67"}}, "title": "Migrate to relocatable CMake package"}, "content": {"raw": "I just updated the drone build to use cmake 2.8.11.2, and it fails, since `target_compile_options` requires cmake 2.8.12\n\n* https://cmake.org/cmake/help/v2.8.12/cmake.html#command:target_compile_options\n* https://cmake.org/cmake/help/v2.8.11/cmake.html doesn't have the command\n\nwe should probably require 2.8.12 instead", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>I just updated the drone build to use cmake 2.8.11.2, and it fails, since <code>target_compile_options</code> requires cmake 2.8.12</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://cmake.org/cmake/help/v2.8.12/cmake.html#command:target_compile_options\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">https://cmake.org/cmake/help/v2.8.12/cmake.html#command:target_compile_options</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://cmake.org/cmake/help/v2.8.11/cmake.html\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">https://cmake.org/cmake/help/v2.8.11/cmake.html</a> doesn't have the command</li>\n</ul>\n<p>we should probably require 2.8.12 instead</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2015-11-19T19:41:46.339334+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef0